V ← ▽⊸≠@J+@A⇡26                    # Valid letters, no J.
K ← ↯5_∞˜⊂▽¬◡˜∊V◴"PLAYFAIREXAMPLE" # Grid from key.
S ← ≡⍜⊣(◿₅+₁)
# Find both chars. Same row; same col; rect.
Pair  ← ⊡⍣(S°1_0|⍜≡⇌S°0_1|⍜⍉⍜⊣⇌◌)⊸/=⊸≡⌟(⊢⊚⌕)
Dedup ← ⍜↻(⊂@X)+1×2⊢
# Ensure: valid letters; no twins; full pairs.
Prep ← ⬚@X↯∞_2 ⍥(⨬◌Dedup>₀⊸⧻⊚≡/=⊸↯∞_2)∞ ▽⊸∊V+¯⊸=@J⌵
Code ← /$"__"≡⌟Pair Prep
"Hide the BIG JAR OF GOLD ⚱️ in ... the tree stump 🪾!"
&pCode⊙(≡⇌⇌K)⊸&pCode⊙K⊸&p
